<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM1.6.3">
<l>cūtiṉaip perukkik kaḷaviṉait tuṇintu</l>
<l>curikuḻal maṭantaiyar tiṟattu</l>
<l>kātalē mikuttuk kaṇṭavā tirinta</l>
<l>toṇṭaṉēṉ namaṉṟamar ceyyum</l>
<l>vētaṉaik koṭuṅki naṭuṅkiṉēṉ vēlai</l>
<l>veṇṭirai yalamarak kaṭainta</l>
<l>nātaṉē vantuṉ tiruvaṭi yaṭaintēṉ</l>
<l>naimicā raṇiyat tuḷentāy.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Intensifying [my] gambling, venturing at theft, and heightening [my] desires</l>
<l rend="indent">toward maids with twisting curls,</l>
<l>I, a slave who wandered haphazardly, trembled, shrinking from the torment</l>
<l rend="indent">that may be inflicted by the minions of Death;</l>
<l>Lord who churned so the sea’s white waves whirled,</l>
<l>Coming [here], I took refuge at your divine feet, my father in Naimiśāraṇyam.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
